    ('CPUC-004', 'XIGMATEK Air Killer S Black CPU Air Cooler Black Nickel Plated Fins 4 Copper Heat-Pipes Direct Touch Technology PWM 12cm ARGB Fan Anti-Vibration Motor Minimizes Vibration And Noise', 'None', 'category3'),
