    ('CPUC-006', 'Thermaltake UX200 SE, 5V Motherboard ARGB Sync 16.8 Million Colors 15 Addressable LED, AMD/Intel (LGA 1700) Universal Socket, Copper Base U-Shape Heatpipes, 170W CPU Cooler CL-P105-AL12SW-A', '800 ~ 1800 RPM, 62.72 CFM, Aluminum & Copper', 'category3'),
